{"tid":748301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【支那屍殺列車】重慶婦列車上突撕咬男乘客 再脫光衣服舔地上血跡","createTime":"2018-07-19T06:07:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T02:12:37.000Z","uid":60398,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"beb7e271f61f49b1dbc43c3e445ea3a1d0880146","tid":748301,"uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T06:07:21.000Z","msg":"今午1時左右，支那重慶軌道交通3號線一名女子突然撕咬旁邊的男乘客，被咬的男乘客滿臉鮮血，車廂內其他乘客被嚇得四處奔逃，該支那女子咬完支那人後，脫光了衣服，還俯臥舔被咬支那乘客的血跡。<br />\n<br />\n據目擊者拍攝的片段可見，支那男乘客被該名支那女子咬得痛苦大叫，隨後用手機砸向支那女子的頭，想要拼命擺脫支那女子，一旁的乘客也都被嚇得不敢向前。在被咬男乘客逃跑後，女子突然開始脫衣服，最後全部脫光。<br />\n<br />\n工作人員稱，列車長發現站台上剛下車的乘客在跑動並大喊「咬人了！」駕駛員立即將車門打開，此時車站工作人員在往6號車廂跑。車長立即查看乘客信息顯示屏，發現6號車廂有名女乘客精神十分異常，於是立即將情況報告。<br />\n<br />\n官方回應指，該女子因與丈夫感情問題導致情緒失控。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">支那預備送大禮 買定午餐肉啊！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/chi/1269393/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Famp%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fchi%2F1269393%2F&d=PmFcvYDdyGly%2FsMPmmCiDQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=cdaac380\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/hd.stheadline.com/amp/news/realtime/chi/1269393/</a>"},{"pid":"018e8f241abe52fce17c85ce7cf71b609c3d35f0","tid":748301,"uid":67500,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T06:08:18.000Z","msg":"用手機插佢個口頂住先"},{"pid":"6c5a0d4df6540c37b04d70a6dd5a2bc679fd40b2","tid":748301,"uid":16061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T06:14:10.000Z","msg":"meth<i